{"tid":1666878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清真寺代表︰林鄭已道歉 信警方非故意","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T07:53:24.000Z","uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"71d8bcd3a6b65083d6a4647c95982a6288cd315f","tid":1666878,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政林鄭月娥及警務處處長盧偉聰到訪清真寺，有伊斯蘭團體代表透露，政府向他們正式道歉，表示警方非故意破壞清真寺。<br />\n<br />\n身穿素色衣服、戴上白色披肩的行政長官林鄭月娥及警務處處長盧偉聰，早上十一時許抵達清真寺，伊斯蘭團體代表在正門迎接。<br />\n<br />\n他們在清真寺逗留約半小時，林鄭月娥及盧偉聰無回答傳媒提問就離開，在場有人示威。<br />\n<br />\n伊斯蘭團體代表透露，林鄭月娥向他們道歉，認為警隊並非故意破壞清真寺及感謝所有替清真寺清潔的人。<br />\n<br />\n警方水炮車昨日在尖沙咀驅散期間噴射藍色水柱，射中清真寺正門。清真寺多處都染有藍色顏料，有市民於昨日下午自發洗刷染有藍色的地下，警員晚上亦到場清潔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2599ee48389b44ac865d41c48a454de6f36150","tid":1666878,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6061902df6f0fe5c73a56c5baa08fd0fc45f5346","tid":1666878,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:21:21.000Z","msg":"停在門口特登射都係非故意"},{"pid":"d72df15f6c9f9164bdae4798b7848e6849b77ec7","tid":1666878,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾popo狗誤射埋巴士站、車公、黃大仙，做咩唔跪埋呀？"},{"pid":"348d4763d8043a963591f63b18bcf552f639fb70","tid":1666878,"uid":49575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit